111
00:20:12,645 --> 00:20:14,306
We'll find him.

112
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:22,720
You know,
you're just like him.

113
00:20:23,356 --> 00:20:25,586
You forget to
remember to be scared.

114
00:20:47,613 --> 00:20:49,274
Can I wait here?

115
00:20:51,184 --> 00:20:52,173
Oh.

116
00:21:06,666 --> 00:21:08,759
