151
00:30:21,987 --> 00:30:23,284
Whoa!

152
00:30:34,466 --> 00:30:38,027
We need your help.
We awakened something.

153
00:30:38,103 --> 00:30:41,834
No. I awakened something.
Something terrible.

154
00:30:51,250 --> 00:30:52,649
That's it!

155
00:31:30,558 --> 00:31:33,220
<i>Today, the Chancellor
presented the latest advancement</i>

156
00:31:33,294 --> 00:31:36,127
