this new technology.</i>

159
00:31:44,239 --> 00:31:48,970
<i>Welcome to the age
of the Machine!</i>

160
00:31:48,971 --> 00:31:52,444
<i>It will create new machines
in its own image!</i>

161
00:31:52,445 --> 00:31:54,378
<i>Machines of peace</i>

162
00:31:54,379 --> 00:31:57,110
