a glorious new era</i>

163
00:31:57,111 --> 00:32:01,913
<i>of wealth and prosperity
for the state!</i>

164
00:32:08,430 --> 00:32:12,264
<i>Residents are advised to
pause for a public address.</i>

165
00:32:14,902 --> 00:32:18,770
<i>Science has turned its
sinister hands against us.</i>

166
00:32:20,307 --> 00:32:22,208
<i>People of our mighty state,</i>

167
00:32:23,277 --> 00:32:28,408
