did you manage to save 2?

189
00:34:24,263 --> 00:34:25,560
Of course not!

190
00:34:25,631 --> 00:34:27,326
By following
this witless folly,

191
00:34:27,399 --> 00:34:29,594
you've endangered
everything we work for!

192
00:34:29,668 --> 00:34:31,602
