to begin with?

193
00:34:31,670 --> 00:34:33,331
I sent him to scout.

194
00:34:33,405 --> 00:34:34,667
That doesn't
make any sense.

195
00:34:34,740 --> 00:34:36,674
You don't send
the oldest out to...

196
00:34:36,742 --> 00:34:39,734
Look, we need to figure out
what's going on.

197
00:34:40,779 --> 00:34:43,646
The source, the source...

198
00:34:45,350 --> 00:34:48,547
Go back to the source.

199
00:34:50,255 --> 00:34:53,247
This is it. This is what
awakened the Machine.

200
00:34:54,526 --> 00:34:56,289
What do you know
about this?

201
00:34:58,063 --> 00:35:02,363
Ah, You can't be trusted.
I won't allow you to endanger us further.

202
00:35:03,368 --> 00:35:04,596
Subjugate them!

203
00:35:04,736 --> 00:35:05,964
Sub... What?

204
00:35:06,038 --> 00:35:08,131
You illiterate cretin!

205
00:35:08,207 --> 00:35:10,072
Take their belongings!

206
00:35:14,313 --> 00:35:15,473
Hey!

207
00:35:22,087 --> 00:35:24,385
You're nothing
but a coward.

208
00:35:27,392 --> 00:35:29,519
How dare you challenge me!

209
00:35:29,595 --> 00:35:32,860
I, who kept everyone
safe all these years.

210
00:35:32,931 --> 00:35:36,423
Ever since you got here,
everything has been unraveling.

211
00:35:36,501 --> 00:35:40,301
You're a curse, a fool,
guided by pointless queries!

212
00:35:40,372 --> 00:35:44,308
And you are a blind man
guided by fear!

213
00:35:49,514 --> 00:35:52,847
Sometimes fear is
the appropriate response.

214
00:36:10,469 --> 00:36:11,902
Whoa!

215
