239
00:43:21,099 --> 00:43:22,464
The source.

240
00:43:22,534 --> 00:43:24,559
The thing that
woke the Machine.

241
00:43:24,636 --> 00:43:27,867
Go back. Go back.
Back to where?

242
00:43:28,239 --> 00:43:30,139
<i>Dark science.</i>

243
00:43:30,809 --> 00:43:34,142
